1)Companies Table
| Column Name   | Description                             |
| ------------- | --------------------------------------- |
| company_id    | Unique ID for the company (Primary Key) |
| company_name  | Legal name of the organization          |
| company_code  | Unique identifier (e.g., FIN-001)       |
| contact_email | Primary business email                  |
| status        | active / suspended / trial              |
| created_at    | Record created time                     |


2)Root Users Table
| Column Name   | Description                 |
| ------------- | --------------------------- |
| root_user_id  | Unique ID for system admin  |
| full_name     | Full name of the root admin |
| username      | Unique login username       |
| password_hash | Encrypted password          |
| email         | Admin contact email         |
| is_active     | System access status        |
| created_at    | Record created time         |

3)Roles Table
| Column Name | Description                              |
| ----------- | ---------------------------------------- |
| role_id     | Unique ID for each role                  |
| company_id  | Linked Company ID (Foreign Key)          |
| role_name   | Role name (Admin, HR, Manager, Employee) |
| description | Details about the role                   |

4)Departments Table
| Column Name     | Description                     |
| --------------- | ------------------------------- |
| department_id   | Unique ID for department        |
| company_id      | Linked Company ID (Foreign Key) |
| department_name | Name of the department          |

5)Employees Table
| Column Name   | Description                     |
| ------------- | ------------------------------- |
| employee_id   | Unique ID for employee          |
| company_id    | Linked Company ID (Foreign Key) |
| employee_code | Employee code                   |
| first_name    | First name                      |
| last_name     | Last name                       |
| email         | Email address                   |
| phone         | Contact number                  |
| gender        | Gender                          |
| date_of_birth | Date of birth                   |
| join_date     | Date of joining                 |
| salary        | Salary                          |
| department_id | Department reference            |
| role_id       | Role reference                  |
| status        | Active / Inactive               |
| created_at    | Record created time             |
| updated_at    | Last updated time               |


6)Users Table
| Column Name   | Description                     |
| ------------- | ------------------------------- |
| user_id       | Unique user ID                  |
| company_id    | Linked Company ID (Foreign Key) |
| employee_id   | Linked employee ID              |
| username      | Login username                  |
| password_hash | Encrypted password              |
| role_id       | User role                       |
| is_active     | Account status                  |
| created_at    | Account created time            |


7)Attendance Table
| Column Name   | Description                     |
| ------------- | ------------------------------- |
| attendance_id | Attendance record ID            |
| company_id    | Linked Company ID (Foreign Key) |
| employee_id   | Employee reference              |
| date          | Attendance date                 |
| check_in      | Check-in time                   |
| check_out     | Check-out time                  |
| status        | Present / Absent / Leave        |
| created_at    | Record created time             |

8) Pages Table (Master List of UI Pages)
| Column Name | Description                                |
| ----------- | ------------------------------------------ |
| page_id     | Unique ID for each page (Primary Key)      |
| page_name   | Human-readable page name (e.g., Dashboard) |
| route_path  | Frontend route path (e.g., /employees)     |
| module_name | Logical module name (e.g., HR, Payroll)    |
| created_at  | Record created time                        |

9) Access Table (Employee â†’ Page Permissions)
| Column Name | Description                                             |
| ----------- | ------------------------------------------------------- |
| access_id   | Unique ID for access record (Primary Key)               |
| company_id  | Linked Company ID (Foreign Key)                         |
| employee_id | Linked Employee ID (Foreign Key)                        |
| page_id     | Linked Page ID (Foreign Key)                            |
| can_view    | Whether employee can view this page (true / false)      |
| can_edit    | Whether employee can edit on this page (true / false)   |
| can_delete  | Whether employee can delete on this page (true / false) |

